name: Fuzzrite
details:
FuzzClassic gnarly garage fuzz. From The Ventures' "2,000 Pound Bee" and Iron Butterfly's "In-A-Gadda-Da-Vida" to the Black Keys, the Fuzzrite has a rich history of taking guitar tones to new levels. We've brought the classic silicon circuit back, and added a 9v power supply.
